### Welcome to The Redlock Republic.
Hello, and welcome to the hub for the Redlock Republic.

### What can I do here?
You can either continue on to the [Forums](http://redlockrepublic.hol.es), or stay on this page to find out more info and news.

### News Center
29/09/2015 13:00 - The new forums are now online!
